They can be awkward.

00:00:18.309 --> 00:00:21.090
You know that moment where you say something
in a group of your friends and it's met with

00:00:21.090 --> 00:00:23.600
a deafening...

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:27.859
That moment that makes you want to grab someone
and shake them saying "I TAKE IT BACK!

00:00:27.859 --> 00:00:31.189
WHATEVER I DID TO MAKE YOU HATE ME I JUST
WANT TO UNDO IT!

00:00:31.189 --> 00:00:32.810
COME BACK TO ME.

00:00:32.810 --> 00:00:37.339
And while they feel like they last eons, turns
out the amount of time it takes to make a

00:00:37.339 --> 00:00:40.020
silence awkward is just four seconds...

00:00:40.020 --> 00:00:42.910
Of course on an Internet video four seconds
seems even longer.

00:00:42.910 --> 00:00:45.269
Case and point: skippable pre-roll ads.

00:00:45.269 --> 00:00:48.339
My beard grows in by the time the skip button
